[toggle title="Our Members"]Our highly educated union sisters and brothers are employedÂ  inÂ  aÂ  wide variety of occupations in the administrative, professional, and technical fields and many are supervisors or managers. Typical occupations include accountants, planners,Â hygienists, IT professionals, management analysts, drafting technicians, and biologists. EAA members are employed in virtually every City department including Police, Fire, Airports, Public Works, and Harbor.[/toggle]
[toggle title="Where our Members Work"]Our members work at hundreds of locations throughout Los Angeles, from San Pedro to the San Fernando Valley, from Boyle Heights to Bel-Air, and from Hollywood to Westwood. When citizens of Los Angeles require any service from the City government, EAA members are involved in providing that service.[/toggle]

